  "tests": [
    {
      "text": "<p>You should have a checkbox <code>input</code> below your <code>label</code> element.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.isNotNull(document.querySelector('fieldset:nth-of-type(3) label + input[type=\"checkbox\"]'));"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Your checkbox <code>input</code> should have an <code>id</code> attribute set to <code>\"recommendation\"</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.strictEqual(document.querySelector(\"fieldset:nth-of-type(3) label + input[type='checkbox']\")?.id, \"recommendation\");"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Your checkbox <code>input</code> should have a <code>name</code> attribute set to <code>\"choice\"</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.strictEqual(document.querySelector(\"fieldset:nth-of-type(3) label + input[type='checkbox']\")?.name, \"choice\");"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Your checkbox <code>input</code> should have a <code>value</code> attribute set to <code>\"recommendation\"</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.strictEqual(document.querySelector(\"fieldset:nth-of-type(3) label + input[type='checkbox']\")?.value, \"recommendation\");"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>You should have a <code>label</code> element below your checkbox <code>input</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.exists(document.querySelector(\"fieldset:nth-of-type(3) input[type='checkbox'] + label:nth-of-type(2)\"));"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Your <code>label</code> element should have the text <code>Personal Recommendation</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.strictEqual(document.querySelector('fieldset:nth-of-type(3) input[type=\"checkbox\"] + label:nth-of-type(2)')?.textContent?.trim(), \"Personal Recommendation\");"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Your <code>label</code> element should have a <code>for</code> attribute set to <code>\"recommendation\"</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.strictEqual(document.querySelector('fieldset:nth-of-type(3) input[type=\"checkbox\"] + label:nth-of-type(2)')?.getAttribute(\"for\"), \"recommendation\");"
    }
  ],
  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Dodajte još jednu prokupljku <code>input</code> sa atributima <code>id</code> i <code>value</code> podešenim na <code>\"recommendation\"</code>, i sa atributom <code>name</code> podešenim na <code>\"choice\"</code>.</p>\n<p>Ispod prokupljke <code>input</code>, dodajte još jedan <code>label</code> sa tekstom <code>Personal Recommendation</code>. Atribut <code>for</code> bi trebalo da bude podešen na <code>\"recommendation\"</code>.</p>\n</section>",
